{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Provides a framework allowing Lua scripts to use a graphical interface, since Reaper has no ability to do so natively. INSTALLATION: After installing this package, you must tell Reaper where to find the library. In the Action List, find and run: "Script: Set Lokasenna_GUI library path.lua"\par}
}

